tags.name: Mukilteo Lighthouse
tags.note: White octagonal tower with red roof, attached to white square building. Lighted throughout 24 hours. HORN: 1 blast ev 30s (3s bl). HORN is activated by keying the mic 5 times on VHF-FM Channel 83A (157.175MHz). HORN will operate for 30 minutes.
tags.seamark:name: Mukilteo Lighthouse

tags.note: This feature is not a contributing structure to the Mukilteo Light which is included in the National Register of Historic Places.
